(1812, 1, '2016-12-06 11:29:52', '2016-12-06 11:29:52', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_gallery type="image_grid" images="4518,4427" img_size="medium"][vc_column_text]SUNDAY BRUNCH @MONTYS\r\nMasih belum punya rencana mau ngapain di hari Minggu Anda? Montys menyuguhkan ide segar yang dapat memanjakan perut dengan paket menu spesial untuk makan siang Anda di hari Minggu. Mereka menawarkan tiga menu utama yang disajikan satu paket dengan segelas Mot &amp; Chandon dan kalau Anda berniat untuk mengajak buah hati, lounge yang terletak di Senopati ini juga memberikan pilihan menu untuk anak-anak Anda yang dilengkapi dengan segelas jus buah segar. Selain itu, Montys baru saja membuat varian baru untuk koleksi signature cocktails mereka, yaitu New Fashion dan Cabe Rawit.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>YOFORIA YOGURT STUDIO</h2>\r\nInspired from the word of yogurt and euphoria, this newly opened yogurt caf aiming to make and spread the yogurt euphoria to Bandung society. Located at the hypest shopping arcade in Bandung, Paris Van Java, you can taste their various yogurt drinks creations made by the chef himself, Chef Martin Natadipraja and some light bites selections, like potato wedges, chicken wings, Gomabo, salmon salad, pannacotta and yogurt smoothie bowl. If you are a coffee sucker, don''t worry, you still can try their espresso that blended well with plain yogurt and caramel, called Yofoccino. So if youre concern about your healthy and your weight, their smoothie bowl and yummy fruit yogurt are the best meals to eat all day.[/vc_column_text][vc_gallery type="image_grid" images="4432,4426" img_size="medium"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'YOFORIA YOGURT STUDIO', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'cultural-tourism-increasing-value-of-destination', '', '', '2017-03-21 04:19:42', '2017-03-21 04:19:42', '', 0, 'http://demo.pixel-industry.com/consultingpress/?p=1812', 0, 'post', '', 0),
