anagement services ConsultingPress provided included definition of clear vision for destination, custom business plan that resulted with positive economical and environmental impacts.\n\n\n\nBy the end of the project, Scuba Diving Philippines increased number of daily visitors by 57%.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][volcanno_heading heading_style="custom-heading-03" title="Activities" title_size="h3"][volcanno_icon_list param_group_default="%5B%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22Connecting%20to%20local%20residents%20and%20travel%20agencies%20to%20enhance%20travelers%20experience%20and%20provide%20them%20with%20important%20information%22%7D%2C%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22Creating%20detailed%20destination%20management%20plan%22%7D%2C%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22Detailed%20destination%20assessment%20and%20new%20tourism%20strategy%20for%20increasing%20number%20of%20visitors%20and%20quality%20of%20service%20they%20receive%22%7D%2C%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22New%20marketing%20and%20branding%20strategy%20creation%20and%20implementation%22%7D%5D"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][volcanno_heading heading_style="custom-heading-03" title="Results" title_size="h3"][volcanno_icon_list param_group_default="%5B%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22Increase%20in%20number%20of%20daily%20visitors%20by%2057%25%22%7D%2C%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22New%20sustainable%20tourism%20strategy%20implementation%20lead%20to%20greater%20awareness%20of%20local%20cultural%20heritage%22%7D%2C%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22E