n and development. Marketing activities helped in creating powerful, recognisable brand across Mallorca and social media networks.\n\n\n\nBy the end of the project, Galeo Tours increased number of new clients by 35%.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][volcanno_heading heading_style="custom-heading-03" title="Activities" title_size="h3"][volcanno_icon_list param_group_default="%5B%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22Connecting%20to%20local%20residents%20and%20travel%20agencies%20to%20enhance%20travelers%20experience%20and%20provide%20them%20with%20important%20information%22%7D%2C%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22Branding%20and%20marketing%22%7D%2C%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22Detailed%20destination%20assessment%20and%20new%20tourism%20strategy%20for%20increasing%20number%20of%20visitors%20and%20quality%20of%20service%20they%20receive%22%7D%2C%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22%5CnNew%20marketing%20and%20branding%20strategy%20creation%20and%20implementation%22%7D%5D"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][volcanno_heading heading_style="custom-heading-03" title="Results" title_size="h3"][volcanno_icon_list param_group_default="%5B%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22Increase%20in%20number%20of%20daily%20visitors%20by%2035%25%22%7D%2C%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22New%20sustainable%20tourism%20strategy%20implementation%20lead%20to%20greater%20awareness%20of%20local%20cultural%20heritage%22%7D%2C%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22Enhanced%20the%20skills%20of%20tourism%20service%20staff%22%7D%2C%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon