bed to 40% in three months and increase of wine bottles sales by 45%. Thats quite impressive result.\n\n\n\nTourism development services ConsultingPress provided included complete destination assessment, creation of tourism master plan, sales plan creation, new product marketing strategies and new visitors attractions planning.\n\n\n\nBy the end of the project, Sicilia White Wine Association increased it''s sales by 65%.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][volcanno_heading heading_style="custom-heading-03" title="Activities" title_size="h3"][volcanno_icon_list param_group_default="%5B%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22Connecting%20to%20local%20residents%20and%20travel%20agencies%20to%20enhance%20travelers%20experience%20and%20provide%20them%20with%20important%20information%22%7D%2C%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22Creating%20detailed%20tourism%20development%20plan%22%7D%2C%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22Detailed%20destination%20assessment%20and%20new%20tourism%20strategy%20for%20increasing%20number%20of%20visitors%20and%20quality%20of%20service%20they%20receive%22%7D%2C%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22New%20marketing%20and%20branding%20strategy%20creation%20and%20implementation%22%7D%5D"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][volcanno_heading heading_style="custom-heading-03" title="Results" title_size="h3"][volcanno_icon_list param_group_default="%5B%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22Increase%20in%20number%20of%20daily%20visitors%20by%2055%25%20and%20sales%20by%2065%25%22%7D%2C%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22New%20sustainable%20tourism%20strategy%20implementation%20lead%20to