ts that will lead to more visitors. By using our tourism consultant tools and services, the projection of increase of number of visitors climbed to 40% in three months. Thats quite impressive result.\n\n\n\nStrategic tourism planning services ConsultingPress provided included complete destination assessment, creation of tourism master plan, new marketing strategies and new visitors attractions planning.\n\n\n\nBy the end of the project, Solis increased number of visitors by 35%.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1483522703396{margin-bottom: 80px !important;}"][vc_column][volcanno_heading heading_style="custom-heading-03" title="Activities" title_size="h3"][volcanno_icon_list param_group_default="%5B%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22Connecting%20to%20local%20residents%20and%20travel%20agencies%20to%20enhance%20travelers%20experience%20and%20provide%20them%20with%20important%20information%22%7D%2C%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22Creating%20detailed%20feasibility%20study%22%7D%2C%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22Detailed%20destination%20assessment%20and%20new%20tourism%20strategy%20for%20increasing%20number%20of%20visitors%20and%20quality%20of%20service%20they%20receive%22%7D%2C%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22New%20marketing%20and%20branding%20strategy%20creation%20and%20implementation%22%7D%5D"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][volcanno_heading heading_style="custom-heading-03" title="Results" title_size="h3"][volcanno_icon_list param_group_default="%5B%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22Increase%20in%20number%20of%20daily%20visitors%20by%2057%25%22%7D%2C%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%2