(1992, 1, '2016-12-08 12:40:46', '2016-12-08 12:40:46', '[vc_row][vc_column][volcanno_single_image reveal="true" image="33"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][volcanno_heading title="Leading Tourism Consulting Company Focused on Sustainable Tourism" subtitle="COMPANY OVERVIEW"][vc_column_text]ConsultingPress is a leading tourism consulting company with over 15 years of experience in tourism strategic planning, tourism marketing and development. ConsultingPress has built its expertise on high-skilled tourism consulting specialists, each in their own field of tourism niche.\n\n\n\nOur main focus is sustainable tourism and how it can help local economy while preserving natural and cultural heritage. Our team of experts has wide experience in fields of cultural heritage marketing, tourism strategic planning, destination marketing and assessment and environmental influence research.\n\n\n\nHere in ConsultingPress we offer our clients support in destination marketing, promoting unique story each destination has and inspiring travellers to visit that destination. Our wide set of tourism consulting services helps our clients in gaining economy boost, cultural heritage promotion and destination promotion, while keeping environment intact.[/vc_column_text][volcanno_feature_box style="feature-box" title="Our mission" text="Helping local businesses create efficient, successful and sustainable tourism business by destination assessment, development, management and marketing."][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][volcanno_heading heading_style="custom-heading-03" title="Why are we different?" animation_param="fadeInUp"][volcanno_icon_list list_style="large-simple" param_group_simple="%5B%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_fontawesome%22%3A%22fa%20fa-gitlab%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-checkmark-2%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22High-skilled%20team%20with%20over%2015%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20tourism%20niche%22%7D%2C%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_ly