(2017, 1, '2016-12-08 13:17:44', '2016-12-08 13:17:44', '[vc_row][vc_column][volcanno_heading heading_style="custom-heading-03" title="Frequently Asked Questions" title_size="h3"][vc_column_text]Here a re a list of some frequently asked questions by our clients. if you dont find the answer you seek, please feel free to contact us.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_tta_accordion style="consulting-press-boxed" color="" active_section="1"][vc_tta_section title="What do you do in ConsultingPress?" tab_id="1479380572185-7af5bf78-e0b7"][vc_column_text]We are leading tourism consulting company oriented on sustainable tourism development, management and marketing. We have high-skilled tourism consultants and partners among travel agencies and independent consultants.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Why sustainable tourism?" tab_id="1479380572204-6e0cbeb5-490f"][vc_column_text]First let''s talk about sustainable tourism meaning. Sustainable tourism doesn''t mean only eco-friendly or green tourism. It''s much more than that. Investing in sustainable tourism you are developing environmental, economic and socio-cultural aspect of your tourism destination. Sustainable tourism helps in preserving cultural heritage, natural resources and helps in economy growth.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="What areas of tourism you cover?" tab_id="1479380659146-4e0c8786-3c2c"][vc_column_text]Here in ConsultingPress we are focused on five main areas of tourism consulting. That is tourism development, strategic planning, tourism marketing and training and education in sustainable tourism management and development.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="How can I join ConsultingPress Team?" tab_id="1480073062948-598a9de0-4e24"][vc_column_text]You are sustainable tourism expert or want to become one of them? Then please submit your CV and cover letter through job application for on our careers page as we are always looking for fresh talent to join our team.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="What Tourism Development Process Involves?" tab_id="1480073128886-e040c4f5-fdef"][vc_column_text]Tourism development process involves couple of inner processes. Those are destination management, workforce development, tourism product development and measurement of tourism impact.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="What Strategic Planning Process Involves?" tab_id="1480073178444-b7d6e6c6-b6ed"][vc_column_text]Strategic planning involves couple of processes and activities like tourism destination assessment, tourism business planning, creating tourism master plan and tourism marketing strategies.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="What is Destination Assessment?" tab_id="1480073219063-003de716-a915"][vc_column_text]By tourism destination assessment we aim to find out what are current destination issues and what are it''s key values for visitors. Destination assessment leads to defining custom strategic plan for tourism destination development and marketing.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Why is tourism marketing important?" tab_id="1480073245648-cfad80ed-e87d"][vc_column_text]Marketing is always one of the most important parts of any business or product. By investing in destination marketing you are increasing acknowledgement of your cultural goods, natural resources and increase the value of your tourism business and products.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'FAQ', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'faq', '', '', '2016-12-08 13:17:44', '2016-12-08 13:17:44', '', 1946, 'http://demo.pixel-industry.com/consultingpress/?page_id=2017', 0, 'page', '', 0),
