(3618, 1, '2016-12-29 11:52:07', '2016-12-29 11:52:07', '[vc_row css=".vc_custom_1482824941562{margin-bottom: 80px !important;}"][vc_column][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1482824910604{margin-bottom: 80px !important;}"]\n\n<h5>Custom dots divider</h5>\n\nThis is example of custom divider in shape of three dots. It is perfect for dividing your content in a beautiful way. Perfect to use on home and intro pages as it adds some custom, unique feel to your page. It''s clean and simple, yet it divides your content in nice way and adds a bit of designers touch to the site. Of course we made some other, simpler dividers you can use on any of your pages. To use a divider, simply add it in a row and full width column inside that row. To use this type of divider just use class "divider".[/vc_column_text][volcanno_divider divider_style="divider"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1482825384714{margin-bottom: 80px !important;}"][vc_column][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1482825393079{margin-bottom: 110px !important;}"]\n\n<h5>Simple Line divider</h5>\n\nThis is example of a simple line divider that divides rows of your content. You can use it on any of your pages, home page or inner pages. To use it, add it in a single row, full width column. Inside of it place a divider element, style line. SImple![/vc_column_text][volcanno_divider divider_style="divider-line"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1482825435126{margin-bottom: 80px !important;}"][vc_column][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1482825404905{margin-bottom: 110px !important;}"]\n\n<h5>Divider dotted</h5>\n\nThis is example of a simple dotted divider that divides rows of your content. You can use it on any of your pages, home page or inner pages. To use it, add it in a single row, full width column. Inside of it place a div with class "divider-dotted".[/vc_column_text][volcanno_divider divider_style="divider-dotted"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1482825445460{margin-bottom: 80px !important;}"][vc_column][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1482825415002{margin-bottom: 110px !important;}"]\n\n<h5>Custom icon divider</h5>\n\nYou can use any of the FontAwesome or Lynny Icons Font icons in this divider. You can use it on any of your pages, home page or inner pages. To use it, add it in a single row, full width column.[/vc_column_text][volcanno_divider divider_style="divider-icon" icon_type="icon_lynny" icon_lynny="lynny-building-2" design_param=".vc_custom_1483001615890{margin-top: 15px !important;}"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1482826288333{margin-bottom: 120px !important;}"][vc_column][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1482825422816{margin-bottom: 110px !important;}"]\n\n<h5>To top divider</h5>\n\nThis is example of to top icon. Normally it is already included in ConsultingPress. You can see it when scrolling down. It appears on the right bottom side of the page. However you may need this element on specific position or specific page, so we decided to include it.[/vc_column_text][volcanno_divider divider_style="divider-scroll-up"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Dividers', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'dividers', '', '', '2016-12-29 11:52:07', '2016-12-29 11:52:07', '', 4346, 'http://demo.pixel-industry.com/consultingpress/?page_id=3618', 0, 'page', '', 0),
