(3636, 1, '2016-12-29 12:03:25', '2016-12-29 12:03:25', '[vc_row][vc_column][volcanno_heading heading_style="custom-heading-02" title="Accordion Default Style" subtitle="SIMPLE ACCORDION FOR YOUR PAGES"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_tta_accordion style="consulting-press-default" color="" active_section="1"][vc_tta_section title="What do you do in ConsultingPress?" tab_id="1477391280657-4ba7f951-bdca"][vc_column_text]\n\n<div class="content clearfix">\n\n\n\nWe are leading tourism consulting company oriented on sustainable tourism development, management and marketing. We have high-skilled tourism consultants and partners among travel agencies and independent consultants.\n\n\n\n</div>\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Why sustainable tourism?" tab_id="1477391280692-04b41938-d83c"][vc_column_text]\n\n<div class="content clearfix">\n\n<div class="content clearfix">\n\n\n\nFirst let''s talk about sustainable tourism meaning. Sustainable tourism doesn''t mean only eco-friendly or green tourism. It''s much more than that. Investing in sustainable tourism you are developing environmental, economic and socio-cultural aspect of your tourism destination. Sustainable tourism helps in preserving cultural heritage, natural resources and helps in economy growth.\n\n\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="What areas of tourism you cover?" tab_id="1480088985228-82abf3c6-6c15"][vc_column_text]\n\n<div class="content clearfix">\n\n\n\nHere in ConsultingPress we are focused on five main areas of tourism consulting. That is tourism development, strategic planning, tourism marketing and training and education in sustainable tourism management and development.\n\n\n\n</div>\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="How can I join ConsultingPress Team?" tab_id="1480089011952-87c6e13b-cf11"][vc_column_text]\n\n<div class="content clearfix">\n\n\n\nYou are sustainable tourism expert or want to become one of them? Then please submit your CV and cover letter through job application for on our careers page as we are always looking for fresh talent to join our team.\n\n\n\n</div>\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_tta_accordion style="consulting-press-default" color="#071740" active_section="1"][vc_tta_section title="What do you do in ConsultingPress?" tab_id="1483617178481-2f70a611-fb5e"][vc_column_text]\n\n<div class="content clearfix">\n\n\n\nWe are leading tourism consulting company oriented on sustainable tourism development, management and marketing. We have high-skilled tourism consultants and partners among travel agencies and independent consultants.\n\n\n\n</div>\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Why sustainable tourism?" tab_id="1483617178567-e3cfebc0-e43b"][vc_column_text]\n\n<div class="content clearfix">\n\n<div class="content clearfix">\n\n\n\nFirst let''s talk about sustainable tourism meaning. Sustainable tourism doesn''t mean only eco-friendly or green tourism. It''s much more than that. Investing in sustainable tourism you are developing environmental, economic and socio-cultural aspect of your tourism destination. Sustainable tourism helps in preserving cultural heritage, natural resources and helps in economy growth.\n\n\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="What areas of tourism you cover?" tab_id="1483617178651-dbe48220-a388"][vc_column_text]\n\n<div class="content clearfix">\n\n\n\nHere in ConsultingPress we are focused on five main areas of tourism consulting. That is tourism development, strategic planning, tourism marketing and training and education in sustainable tourism management and development.\n\n\n\n</div>\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="How can I join ConsultingPress Team?" tab_id="1483617178743-ade7a1b1-9799"][vc_column_text]\n\n<div class="content clearfix">\n\n\n\nYou are sustainable tourism expert or want to become one of them? Then please submit your CV and cover letter through job application for on our careers page as we are always looking for fresh talent to join our team.\n\n\n\n</div>\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][volcanno_heading heading_style="custom-heading-02" title="Accordion Boxed Style" subtitle="ACCORDION BOXED STYLE, USED ON FAQ PAGE"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_tta_accordion style="consulting-press-boxed" color="" active_section="1"][vc_tta_section title="What Tourism Development Process Involves?" tab_id="1477391365631-111b0fd4-196f"][vc_column_text]\n\n<div id="1477391280657-4ba7f951-bdca" class="vc_tta-panel vc_active" data-vc-content=".vc_tta-panel-body">\n\n<div class="vc_tta-panel-body">\n\n<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">\n\n<div class="wpb_wrapper">\n\n<div class="content clearfix">\n\n<div class="content clearfix">\n\n<div class="content clearfix">\n\n\n\nTourism development process involves couple of inner processes. Those are destination management, workforce development, tourism product development and measurement of tourism impact.\n\n\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="What Strategic Planning Process Involves?" tab_id="1477391365704-2e3fe252-4c9c"][vc_column_text]\n\n<div class="content clearfix">\n\n<div class="content clearfix">\n\n\n\nStrategic planning involves couple of processes and activities like tourism destination assessment, tourism business planning, creating tourism master plan and tourism marketing strategies.\n\n\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="What is Destination Assessment?" tab_id="1480089281821-684fb275-f67c"][vc_column_text]\n\n<div class="content clearfix">\n\n\n\nBy tourism destination assessment we aim to find out what are current destination issues and what are it''s key values for visitors. Destination assessment leads to defining custom strategic plan for tourism destination development and marketing.\n\n\n\n</div>\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_tta_accordion style="consulting-press-boxed" color="#071740" active_section="1"][vc_tta_section title="What Tourism Development Process Involves?" tab_id="1483617287304-cc5d6ccd-6814"][vc_column_text]\n\n<div id="1477391280657-4ba7f951-bdca" class="vc_tta-panel vc_active" data-vc-content=".vc_tta-panel-body">\n\n<div class="vc_tta-panel-body">\n\n<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">\n\n<div class="wpb_wrapper">\n\n<div class="content clearfix">\n\n<div class="content clearfix">\n\n<div class="content clearfix">\n\n\n\nTourism development process involves couple of inner processes. Those are destination management, workforce development, tourism product development and measurement of tourism impact.\n\n\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="What Strategic Planning Process Involves?" tab_id="1483617287401-7def4c45-131c"][vc_column_text]\n\n<div class="content clearfix">\n\n<div class="content clearfix">\n\n\n\nStrategic planning involves couple of processes and activities like tourism destination assessment, tourism business planning, creating tourism master plan and tourism marketing strategies.\n\n\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="What is Destination Assessment?" tab_id="1483617287485-94e655b8-0598"][vc_column_text]\n\n<div class="content clearfix">\n\n\n\nBy tourism destination assessment we aim to find out what are current destination issues and what are it''s key values for visitors. Destination assessment leads to defining custom strategic plan for tourism destination development and marketing.\n\n\n\n</div>\n\