(4428, 1, '2017-03-20 05:03:26', '2017-03-20 05:03:26', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>Amazing Sites on Croatian Coast That Are Worth Visiting</h2>\r\nHave you ever been to Croatia? Here are ten good reasons to visit Croatia this summer.\r\n\r\nCroatia is a small but beautiful country situated in Europe with crystal clear Adriatic sea. It''s full of amazing beaches, cultural attractions and amazing sites.[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>Some of Croatia''s best attractions</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][volcanno_icon_list param_group_default="%5B%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22Dubrovnik%20Old%20Town.%20Ever%20heard%20of%20Dubrovnik%3F%20You%20know%2C%20that%20place%20on%20the%20coast%20where%20they%20filmed%20the%20Game%20of%20Thrones%3F%20Well%20you%20should.%20It''s%20a%20great%20place%20to%20visit%2C%20with%20exquisite%20restaurants%2C%20cultural%20sites%2C%20amazing%20beaches%20and%20of%20course%20Game%20of%20Thrones%20series%20original%20throne%20is%20there%20and%20you%20can%20see%20it%2C%20take%20photos%20and%20make%20remarkable%20memories!%22%7D%2C%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22Split.%20What''s%20so%20great%20about%20Split%3F%20Well%20it''s%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20cities%20on%20Croatian%20coast%2C%20host%20of%20mega%20popular%20Ultra%20festival%2C%20amazing%20cultural%20heritage%2C%20beaches%2C%20night%20clubs%20and%20bars%2C%20everything%20you%20can%20imagine%20is%20there.%22%7D%2C%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22The%20Sea%20Organ%20of%20Zadar.%20Want%20to%20listen%20beautiful%20sounds%20of%20the%20waves%20and%20sea%3F%20Seriously%20if%20you%20haven''t%20been%20to%20Zadar%20to%20hear%20The%20Sea%20Organ%20you%20need%20to!%20It''s%20first%20attraction%20in%20the%20world%20of%20that%20kind!%22%7D%2C%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22Opatija.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20beautiful%20and%20popular%20places%20in%20Istria%2C%20with%20exquisite%20cuisine%2C%20beautiful%20hotels%20and%20beaches.%20Also%20one%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20business%20destinations.%22%7D%2C%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22And%20so%20many%20more...%20I%20could%20write%20about%20it%20all%20day%20long...%22%7D%5D" design_param=".vc_custom_1481025883782{padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"][vc_column_text]If these few sounds interesting head over to youtube and see some videos. I think you will be thrilled. Also make sure you see some of the less popular parts of Croatia - Zagorje which is full of amazing medieval castles and exquisite cuisine and rich cultural heritage. Towns that are worth visiting, among other are Trakoan with amazing castle, Varadin - small barouque town with beautiful architecture, and of course Zagreb, main capital.\r\n\r\nAlso one great part of Croatia is Slavonija. Beautiful part in East Croatia, characteristic by traditional cuisine and one of the best wine cellars in the world. Also make sure to visit Vinkovci, the oldest town in whole Europe.\r\n\r\nThere is so much to see in that beautiful country. Like "Emilia Clarke" said in her interview about Croatia, what she likes: Food, Culture, People... So make sure to put it in your travel calendar![/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', '10 Good Reasons to Visit Croatian Coast This Summer', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1824-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-20 05:03:26', '2017-03-20 05:03:26', '', 1824, 'http://localhost/fix-theme-fashion/1824-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
