(4431, 1, '2017-03-20 05:04:59', '2017-03-20 05:04:59', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>Increasing Tourism Destination Value by Investing in Cultural Tourism</h2>\r\nCultural tourism plays great importance in destination management and tourism marketing. Thtis is why sustainable tourism is so important in today''s world and tourism business.[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>Sustainable tourism is one of the great new approaches to tourism development as it helps in:</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][volcanno_icon_list param_group_default="%5B%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22Increase%20the%20numbers%20of%20daily%20visitors%22%7D%2C%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22New%20sustainable%20tourism%20strategy%20implementation%20lead%20to%20greater%20awareness%20of%20local%20cultural%20heritage%22%7D%2C%7B%22icon_type%22%3A%22icon_lynny%22%2C%22icon_lynny%22%3A%22lynny-record%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22Perfect%20harmony%20of%20environmental%2C%20social%20and%20economical%20tourism%20sectors%22%7D%5D" design_param=".vc_custom_1481024791369{padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\nTourism is one of the largest and fastest growing industries in the world, which is why sustainable tourism is so important. It helps to conserve cultural heritage and preserve nature in the same time. Every destination has its own unique story and practicing sustainable tourism, you give that unique story much more important place in marketing, destination planning and assessment and of course you have long term benefits.\r\n\r\nPreserving cultural heritage is very important. By cultural heritage we mean all kinds of human creations across the globe. It means all aspects of human history. By marketing your cultural heritage in appropriate way, you are inviting tourists, that is visitors to visit and explore your destination and society. It gives personal experience and leaves long term impact on both the visitor and local economy.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Cultural Tourism: Increasing Value of Destination', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1812-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-20 05:04:59', '2017-03-20 05:04:59', '', 1812, 'http://localhost/fix-theme-fashion/1812-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
